[pscustomobject]@{title='P2 Storage: BufferPool frame lifecycle (load/evict/dirty)'; body='## Parent Epic`nPhase 2 (Weeks 5-6): Data Storage Foundation`n`n## Scope`nImplement frame management in buffer pool.`n`n## Tasks`n- Implement page load into frame`n- Track dirty/clean state`n- Implement eviction flow with write-back`n- Add frame table bookkeeping`n`n## Acceptance Criteria`n- Dirty pages are flushed before eviction`n- Frame lifecycle tests pass'}
