[pscustomobject]@{title='P2 Catalog: CREATE TABLE execution path'; body='## Parent Epic`nPhase 2 (Weeks 7-8): Table Management System`n`n## Scope`nImplement CREATE TABLE flow from command to metadata persistence.`n`n## Tasks`n- Parse/validate create table input`n- Create catalog entry`n- Create physical table backing structure`n- Return success/error response`n`n## Acceptance Criteria`n- CREATE TABLE creates catalog + storage artifacts`n- Duplicate table name returns expected error'}
