[pscustomobject]@{title='P2 CRUD: CRUD end-to-end tests with fixture datasets'; body='## Parent Epic`nPhase 2 (Weeks 9-10): Basic CRUD Operations`n`n## Scope`nAdd E2E tests covering insert/select/filter flows.`n`n## Tasks`n- Create fixture datasets`n- Add E2E tests for insert + select + where`n- Add restart scenario to verify persistence`n`n## Acceptance Criteria`n- E2E tests pass locally and in CI`n- Failures provide actionable diagnostics'}
