[pscustomobject]@{title='P2 Parser: AST node definitions for CREATE/INSERT/SELECT'; body='## Parent Epic`nPhase 2 (Weeks 11-12): SQL Parser Foundation`n`n## Scope`nDefine AST structures for supported SQL statements.`n`n## Tasks`n- Add base AST node interfaces/types`n- Define CREATE TABLE AST nodes`n- Define INSERT and SELECT AST nodes`n`n## Acceptance Criteria`n- AST can represent MVP SQL subset`n- AST construction tests pass'}
[pscustomobject]@{title='P2 Parser: Parser for CREATE TABLE'; body='## Parent Epic`nPhase 2 (Weeks 11-12): SQL Parser Foundation`n`n## Scope`nImplement parser branch for CREATE TABLE statements.`n`n## Tasks`n- Parse table name and column definitions`n- Parse data types and constraints subset`n- Build CREATE AST nodes`n`n## Acceptance Criteria`n- Valid CREATE statements parse successfully`n- Invalid syntax returns structured parse errors'}
